{"tid":2288257,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陸偉雄: 網民熱心響應眾籌致款項超出預期並不違法 對警方以洗黑錢之名拉人感到奇怪","createTime":"2020-11-16T11:11:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T12:23:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7598ff38e7f3fd35770bd43fc54b9c2f4d26a8f2","tid":2288257,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:11:29.000Z","msg":"大律師陸偉雄指出，眾籌並不犯法。根據「洗黑錢」的定義，涉嫌人士必須要知道收取的款項是犯罪得益，或有所懷疑卻仍然接受。發起眾籌者，如有合法目的，而熱心網民相繼將錢存入戶口，即使最後籌到的款項，比他所述的多，這亦與他無關，更何況若眾籌者再發文終止籌款，最後籌到多少錢，這不是他控制到，可說是與他無關。<br />\n<br />\n因此警方以洗黑錢之名拉人，陸偉雄感到奇怪，需求證警方是甚麼理據，希望再作進一步交代。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201116/H6OCS4U7ARF5ZDZZAHXWUD3N7Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201116%2FH6OCS4U7ARF5ZDZZAHXWUD3N7Y%2F&d=Mbax9TUBBsNKvtRo7%2B5fu1TAjexNHzxSh3iQmMoU3XE%3D&h=fbc157be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201116%2FH6OCS4U7ARF5ZDZZAHXWUD3N7Y%2F&h=42d51ed1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201116/H6OCS4U7ARF5ZDZZAHXWUD3N7Y/</a>"},{"pid":"39c0a39ad98119a23322f5b679a983439047a0af","tid":2288257,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:13:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75ec40d045897b413a2327df3833636a4bcebc45","tid":2288257,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:14:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc99fb258cb28d41c83316d2453b64377553298d","tid":2288257,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"h